Package: track2sample
Type: Package
Title: Choose and apply a distance threshold to convert a track to samples
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paulo Correa
Maintainer: Paulo Correa <correapvf@gmail.com>
Description: This package will help to select and apply a distance threshold
	for subdividng a track data in multiple segments of same length for ecological analysis.
